```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many dogs are in the image?')

ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is one dog clearly older than the other?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is one dog clearly older than the other?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 2 and {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} == 2 and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
